{"tid":485686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海牙法庭判監二十年    克裔軍官當場飲鴆自盡","createTime":"2017-12-01T07:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T09:38:15.000Z","uid":76115,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aea2a602173cd34e2abe0e731359eddd2b3088ff","tid":485686,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/SF38ct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FSF38ct&d=EsbRmfGEyIqgtGSc2fR%2Bh5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=1a26af6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/SF38ct</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/137735/thumbnail/6715e0b6508a3ad5e47d1bf6fa075085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F137735%2Fthumbnail%2F6715e0b6508a3ad5e47d1bf6fa075085.jpg&h=77ef99bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭海牙聯合國國際戰爭法庭正就6名在波斯尼亞戰爭時犯下戰爭罪行的克羅地亞裔前軍官進行二審。波斯尼亞前軍方司令普拉利亞克（Slobodan Praljak）因不滿裁決判他入獄20年，周三（11月29日）當場服毒。他3小時後死亡。克羅地亞總理普連科維奇（Andrej Plenkovic）表示震驚及哀悼，並譴責法庭裁決不公。<br />\n<br />\n事發時普拉利亞克從口袋中拿出玻璃瓶，當場喝下瓶內液體，更指出這是毒藥。他大叫：「我不是戰犯，反對判決結果。」他生前已被囚13年，若他仍生還，不久後便可假釋出獄。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1021122/xlarge/4952ddd1c555f235b4b55afd5d7fe3ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1021122%2Fxlarge%2F4952ddd1c555f235b4b55afd5d7fe3ed.jpg&h=ad9ee043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波斯尼亞前軍方司令普拉利亞克（Slobodan Praljak）因不滿前南斯拉夫國際戰犯法庭（ICTY）判他入獄20年，當場服毒，3小時後死亡。他死後，波黑的莫斯塔爾（Mostar）在周三（11月29日）有民眾舉行悼念活動。莫斯塔爾是普拉利亞克的故鄉。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n普拉利亞克之死令的克羅地亞民眾同樣震驚，在他故鄉莫斯塔爾（Mostar），有人自發舉行悼念活動。 <br />\n<br />\n終年72歲的普拉利亞克與其他5名同案被告，涉嫌在1992至1995年波斯尼亞爆發內戰期間，對波斯尼亞穆斯林進行種族清洗，對他們予以驅逐及迫害。<br />\n<br />\n這是首次有被告在前南斯拉夫國際戰犯法庭（International Criminal Tribunal for the former Yugoslavia，ICTY）上自殺。荷蘭警方已就事件展開調查，以了解他如何取得毒液，以及怎樣帶進法庭。有律師指出，法庭保安人員針對金屬物品及手機進行檢查，藥丸以及少量液體不在管制範圍。"},{"pid":"8fca6d6a380a5ff3e82a3f7fc118fe8e21b545b1","tid":485686,"uid":102642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"無聲哭訴"},{"pid":"d06dcf8492d2edd09d6c4fc6cd2818f397e4da05","tid":485686,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"種族清洗？"},{"pid":"50a982d908c3913df6368dfc44c90020ed919dac","tid":485686,"uid":132038,"like":44,"dislike":9,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5520304b9220b0163633c8a912afb61b69f280e2","tid":485686,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"保鏢救殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcc8a9077e6c8a4a61eaa23c7bd737a0cd21959","tid":485686,"uid":28031,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"戰爭罪行呢樣野真係好白痴 <br />\n蔣介石 林肯 哥倫布就係偉人<br />\n前線兵就要上庭"},{"pid":"8c5c55660f59ec0056dcf462ca0594be3c18ef18","tid":485686,"uid":1773,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真打仗唔係你殺我就我殺你架啦,班仆街左膠玩秋後算帳依加累到人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種族清洗係另一回事wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通納粹集中營又可以當冇事?"},{"pid":"072aeaac335cc0afc2329c61492220767391e1be","tid":485686,"uid":14625,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真打仗唔係你殺我就我殺你架啦,班仆街左膠玩秋後算帳依加累到人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小朋友唔知咩叫genocide?"},{"pid":"3ca0ca59001250df213c534daf377c2768ffe138","tid":485686,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰爭罪行呢樣野真係好白痴 <br />\n蔣介石 林肯 哥倫布就係偉人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線兵就要上庭</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 